  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 384
  - Title: Monkey
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Steadfastness
---
During the course of your journey you will at all times enjoy the
assistance of spiritual beings, who will see to it that you do not
succumb to the perils that will beset you on your path.
